CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FHospital admissions from spider bites
OL,8,Fhave doubled in England in the last
OL,9,Fdecade, with experts blaming the rise
OL,10,Fon the "explosion" in the population
OL,11,Fof false widows.
OL,13,FProvisional NHS figures show there
OL,14,Fwere 100 admissions as a result of
OL,15,F"contact with or toxic effect of
OL,16,Fspiders" in 2025 compared with 47 in
OL,17,F2015, a freedom of information request
OL,18,Fobtained has revealed.
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@RO]wD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FAcademics have linked the rise to the
OL,8,Fincrease in the noble false widow
OL,9,Fspider, a species described as "the
OL,10,Fmost dangerous spider breeding in
OL,11,FBritain" in a 2020 paper by Oxford
OL,12,FUniversity ecologist Clive Hambler.
OL,14,FThe species, which is known to bite,
OL,15,Foriginates from Madeira and the Canary
OL,16,FIslands and was first reported in
OL,17,Fsouthern England in 1879.
OL,26,@qD@`OUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FMr Hambler, who is a lecturer in
OL,8,Fbiological and human sciences at
OL,9,FHertford College, said: "The days when
OL,10,Fyou could just treat spiders as benign
OL,11,Fin Britain are over".
OL,13,F"I think if you were going back 50
OL,14,Fyears, then there would have been
OL,15,Fhardly any consequences from spider
OL,16,Fbites in Britain," he said.
OL,26,@qD@YOUsD@TO]uD@AOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,F"The incidents of severe bites from
OL,8,Fspiders in Britain will have
OL,9,Fincreased, as this species (false
OL,10,Fwidows) became hugely more abundant in
OL,11,FBritain, particularly in the south."
OL,13,FThere were 43 hospital admissions due
OL,14,Fto spider bites in 2021, and the
OL,15,Ffigure increased to 95 the following
OL,16,Fyear, the NHS figures show. In both
OL,17,F2023 and 2024, there were 91
OL,18,Fadmissions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FMr Hambler said that people are coming
OL,8,Finto contact with false widow spiders
OL,9,Fmuch more often than they realise,
OL,10,Fadding that he has seen the species in
OL,11,Fthe gardens of Buckingham Palace.
OL,13,FHe explained that the venom in the
OL,14,Fbites can cause pain and itching but
OL,15,Fthe more serious toxic effects are due
OL,16,Fto the bacteria carried by the spider
OL,17,F` which he said can potentially lead
OL,18,Fto "amputation, sepsis and death".
OL,26,@zD@DOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FThe academic said the species is "much
OL,8,Fmore willing to bite than many people
OL,9,Fare willing to admit" and that he
OL,10,Fsuspects that many people per day are
OL,11,Fbeing bitten.
OL,13,FMr Hambler said the public should be
OL,14,Fmore aware of the risks that false
OL,15,Fwidows pose without being alarmed.
OL,26,@oD@bOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FHe said: "I think spiders are
OL,8,Fwonderful things and they're very
OL,9,Fimportant in ecosystems, but you now
OL,10,Fneed to treat spiders in Britain as
OL,11,Fyou might in many other parts of the
OL,12,Fworld ` as something to be very
OL,13,Frespectful of.
OL,15,F"I mean it's a balance because people
OL,16,Fwill say 'oh you'll cause
OL,17,Farachnophobia', but I don't think many
OL,18,Fpeople are going to die of
OL,19,Farachnophobia in Britain but they will
OL,20,Fdie from this thing."
OL,26,@oD@JOUwD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FMr Hambler said there are a number of
OL,8,Freasons why the hospital admissions
OL,9,Fmight have increased in the last 10
OL,10,Fyears, including the fact that medics
OL,11,Fare becoming more alert to the fact of
OL,12,Fspider bites and there are more people
OL,13,Fin Britain.
OL,15,FThe figures reveal that of the 100
OL,16,Fadmissions in 2025, 73 of these were
OL,17,Fthrough the A&E department. This
OL,18,Fcompares to 38 of the 47 in 2015.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FDr Michel Dugon, a zoologist
OL,8,Fspecialising in the evolution and
OL,9,Fdevelopment of venom systems at the
OL,10,FUniversity of Galway, said the figures
OL,11,Fare "interesting" but "not surprising".
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FHe added that the "most obvious"
OL,19,Ffactor that might have caused the rise
OL,20,Fis the "explosion in the population of
OL,21,Fnoble false widow".
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@QO]sD@WOUsD@fO]zD@SOUzD@`O]|D@
OL,26,AHOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,F"We know that those species indeed can
OL,8,Factually bite, that they do have a
OL,9,Fpreference to live in and around
OL,10,Fhouses rather than in natural
OL,11,Fhabitats, at least in the UK and
OL,12,FIreland," he said.
OL,14,FDr Dugon said that with increased
OL,15,Fmedia coverage on false widows and
OL,16,Fspider bites over the last few years,
OL,17,Fsome people might have come forward
OL,18,Fbelieving they have been bitten by the
OL,19,Fspecies when it may have been
OL,20,Fsomething else.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,F"Essentially, when you do not see the
OL,8,Fspider really bite or capture the
OL,9,Fspider and you say that you haven't
OL,10,Ffelt any pain ` then it's most likely
OL,11,Fnot a spider," he added.
OL,13,F"Because a bite by the noble false
OL,14,Fwidow will actually wake you up. The
OL,15,Fpain is equivalent to a wasp sting or
OL,16,Feven more than that."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@NO]uD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FDr Dugon said that spiders are "not
OL,8,Faggressive animals" and "don't
OL,9,Fparticularly try to bite", adding that
OL,10,F100 cases in England is relatively
OL,11,Fminor.
OL,13,FAdam Hart, a professor of science
OL,14,Fcommunication at the University of
OL,15,FGloucestershire, said that while false
OL,16,Fwidows have "expanded their range",
OL,17,Fthere is no strong reason for the
OL,18,Fpublic to be concerned about the
OL,19,Fspecies.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@SO]pD@YOUqD@YO]xD@MOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776059756
OL,3,CFalse Widow spread responsible for
OL,4,C'doubling of spider bite hospital
OL,5,Cadmissions'
OL,7,FHe said: "While they can bite if
OL,8,Fhandled or trapped against the skin,
OL,9,Fmost bites are mild and severe
OL,10,Freactions are rare.
OL,12,F"Basic precautions, such as not
OL,13,Fhandling spiders directly, should
OL,14,Fensure the chances of being bitten are
OL,15,Fminuscule."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
